ygData.msgSnippet: At 25 26, PC becomes a bit small but I think M Saru off of Neth lair is good as well from 25-28 or so, but High keep is Dabomb at that level. Good Luck ...
ygData.messageBody:
At 25 26, PC becomes a bit small but I think M Saru
off of Neth lair is good as well from 25-28 or so, but
High keep is Dabomb at that level.

Good Luck
